{
  "stem": "2118.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans selected the [NON-ENGLISH] of the Juden, which means the oldest of the Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It has two meanings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, he happened to be an old man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the meaning didn't mean because he's old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It means he is the [NON-ENGLISH], the oldest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Chaim [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Romkowski. ?] He was-- he was running [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, for children, a-- children without parents-- orphanage before the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was not a man off the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was, you know, he was-- he was an [? old ?] person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have seen him many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not know him, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never came to-- to speak to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just a boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll come to that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did what-- we did-- my father was still working in his own little shop, making a few marks here, a few marks there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I paid him a little this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I paid him-- And while the committee, or the [NON-ENGLISH], was organizing, they set up some resorts, what they called, which means a place to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not a resort [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shops, resort shops.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they needed people to help set up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father would go and fix some machine or do little things, you know, which had to be done, for himself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the people who ran that thing, the committee, they could pay out a certain amount of money to private persons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they put people to work for the German army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That started out right in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And people started to plant little plots with greens and things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was helping my father, you know-- carry things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no transportation, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You had to deliver something, you had to carry it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
